Cell A15 | value='stage18' | fill=FF00B050 | rows=[14] | cols=[0] | col_header=False | row_header=True | metadata=False
Cell B15 | value='Successional stage designation for 2018.' | fill=00000000 | rows=[14] | cols=[1] | col_header=False | row_header=False | metadata=False
Cell A16 | value='change8808' | fill=FF00B050 | rows=[15] | cols=[0] | col_header=False | row_header=True | metadata=False
Cell B16 | value='Benthic habitat change trends for 1988-2008 were assigned by comparing the Successional Stage descriptors for those time periods. Trends indicate that the biotope changed and/or there was evidence of higher successional stage. Improved: Any portion of the 2018 Successional Stage descriptor is higher than in 2008. Remained good quality: The highest portion of the Successional Stage descriptor present in 2008 is still present in 2018 (e.g., a change from Stage 2 on 3 to Stage 1 on 3). Remained poor quality: A Successional Stage less than 2 is present in both years. Declined: Any portion of the 2018 Successional Stage descriptor is lower than in 2008 AND the 2018 Successional Stage is below 2. Change status not determined: Change status was not determined if there was insufficient information.' | fill=00000000 | rows=[15] | cols=[1] | col_header=False | row_header=False | metadata=False
